* GP2X <strong>[*]</strong> [http://wiki.gp2x.org/wiki/OpenTTD]
* Nokia N-series (Maemo) <strong>[*]</strong> [http://myy.haaga-helia.fi/~a0702483/maemo/] e[http://www.tt-forums.net/viewtopic.php?f=33&t=36042] (di [http://openttd.toimii.net/maemo/])
* [[it/Nintendo DS|Nintendo DS]] <strong>[*]</strong> [http://www.tt-forums.net/viewtopic.php?f=33&t=35306]
* Pocket PC <strong>[*]</strong> [http://www.esoftinteractive.com/openttd.html]
* PSP <strong>[*]</strong> [http://openttd.pc-workshop.da.ru/]
* UIQ3 <strong>[*]</strong> [http://my-symbian.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30981]
* Zaurus PDA <strong>[*]</strong> [http://zsi2.stonekeep.com/index.php?v=d&a=2127]

Sono inoltre in corso dei tentativi per svilouppare una [[it/Versione per dispositivi mobili|versione unificata per dispositivi mobili]].

